  | accessdate = 2 December 2006}}</ref> According to the 6 pm [[channel 4]] (9 December 2006) news the intake of polonium she suffered will only result in a dose of 100 mSv. This will lead to a 1 in 200 chance of [[cancer]].

; [[Akhmed Zakayev]] : The [[Forensics|forensic investigation]] also includes the silver Mercedes by Litvinenko's home believed to be owned by his close friend and neighbour [[Akhmed Zakayev]], then [[foreign minister]] of the separatist [[government in exile]] of [[Chechen Republic of Ichkeria|Ichkeria]].<ref>{{cite web
