* [[Channel 4|Channel Four Television Corporation]] has signed Mentorn productions to make a television drama based on the Litvinenko poisoning. [[Peter Kosminsky]] will be the director.<ref>{{cite web
  | title =Daybreak Pictures Commissioned To Produce Litvinenko Poisoning Drama
