* [[Thriller (genre)|Thriller]] writers [[Frederick Forsyth]] and [[Andy McNab]] claimed that the killing of Alexander Litvinenko is a classic case of fact being stranger than fiction and that they would be fighting a losing battle if they offered a Litvinenko-style story to a publisher.<ref>{{cite web
